can you help me figure out why this app doesn't work? It works on my machine. So yeah, this

00:04:29.559 --> 00:04:34.559
talk is aimed to briefly skirt over some of the more common root causes that I've seen

00:04:34.559 --> 00:04:41.399
in my role. So how do you know when a car is having problems? If you turn the ignition

00:04:41.399 --> 00:04:47.079
and it doesn't start, that's probably a pretty good indicator. You might also see some warning

00:04:47.079 --> 00:04:51.720
lights on your dashboard, that's usually a sign that something is wrong. If you have

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:55.279
a bit of know‑how, there are a bunch of things you can check yourself under the hood

