00:12:43.099 --> 00:12:46.340
appropriate resources would lead to a sluggish performance. It's kind of like imagine this

00:12:46.340 --> 00:12:55.340
car had a small engine, it wouldn't perform as well in a race.

00:12:56.340 --> 00:13:03.739
So system resources. Just how you can tune a car's engine to run optimally. As a developer,

